de.intarsys.security.smartcard.card

Interface ICloseCallback


  • public interface ICloseCallback
    The ICloseCallback is used to inform client code about the result of an asynchronous attempt to close a ICardConnection. You should never use blocking code, at least not attempting to reference the ICard in one of the callback methods.
